<em>Published in final edited form as: </em>Osteoporos Int. 2012 Jun 6;24(2):671–680. doi: <a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s00198-012-2043-5" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">10.1007/s00198-012-2043-5</a>
